		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://elliottback.com/wp/why-my-wordpress-site-is-so-much-faster-than-yours/#comment-2194521">10/16/2010 at 3:55 pm</a></div>

		<p>[...] at WebFaction, it was stupidly easy to set up. I also read some great articles, including this one, about performance considerations and [...]</p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='/wp/why-my-wordpress-site-is-so-much-faster-than-yours/?replytocom=2194521#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-2194521", "2194521", "respond", "2199")'>Reply</a>		</div>
