		<p>This is one of the pages I used as I got started with my new hosting environment.  I settled on nginx as the web server, APC OpCode cache, and rather than use the WP-SuperCache plugin, I stuck Varnish in front of the whole works.</p>
<p>Thanks for the great post!  and I look forward to reading more.</p>

